column4: The awarded loans will settle on November 5, 2009, and will mature on January 14, 2010. The stop-out rate shown above will apply to all awarded loans.
column5: Institutions that submitted winning bids will be contacted by their respective Reserve Banks by 11:30 a.m. EST on November 3, 2009. Participants have until 12:30 p.m. EST on November 3, 2009, to inform their local Reserve Bank of any error.
